---
// Hero.astro - 主页 Hero 区域
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center pt-24 pb-16 px-4 section-enter">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center">
    <!-- 标签 -->
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-claude-primary/10 border border-claude-primary/20 text-claude-primary text-sm mb-8">
      <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
        <path d="M11 3a1 1 0 10-2 0v1a1 1 0 102 0V3zM15.657 5.757a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414l-.707.707a1 1 0 001.414 1.414l.707-.707zM18 10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a1 1 0 110-2h1a1 1 0 011 1zM5.05 6.464A1 1 0 106.464 5.05l-.707-.707a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l.707.707zM5 10a1 1 0 01-1 1H3a1 1 0 110-2h1a1 1 0 011 1z"/>
        <path d="M10 18a3 3 0 100-6 3 3 0 000 6z"/>
      </svg>
      Claude Code 官方文档指南 + 官方 Skills 仓库解析
    </div>

    <!-- 标题 -->
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-6">
      <span class="gradient-text">Agent Skills</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- 副标题 -->
    <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      让 Claude 学会你的工作方式——自动匹配专业知识，无需记忆命令
    </p>

    <!-- CTA 按钮 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="#create-skill" class="px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-claude-primary to-claude-secondary rounded-xl font-semibold hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity cursor-pointer">
        开始创建
      </a>
      <a href="#official-skills" class="explore-official-btn px-8 py-4 bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors cursor-pointer">
        探索官方 Skills
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
